  <brief_title>A Non-interventional Study Evaluating the Clinical Benefit and Effectiveness of Quetiapine Fumarate Extended</brief_title>
  <acronym>CLIMAX</acronym>
  <official_title>A Non-interventional Study Evaluating the Clinical Benefit and Effectiveness of Quetiapine Fumarate Extended-Release Tablets (SEROQUEL XRÃ¢) in Subjects With Schizophrenia-An Observational, Multicentric Prospective Study</official_title>
