  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this NIS is to assess the clinical benefit subjects derive from
      taking seroquel XR, using the CGI-CB. The secondary objective is to assess the
      effectiveness,safety and tolerability of seroquel XR tablets.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
